spanGrp.span: When our people were living there it was very good in our village.
bizım halh yašianda čoğ yahšiidi hä
eddi kissä var orda edditälä edditänä kissä var
Now I can’t describe every church.
šindi saimainan äpsıni šindi diamerım bän ki angısi angısidır
There was a river next to the village.
čay varıdi kövün yanında čay gečerdi hä
yahši šei varıdi vozduh nätävür dierlär hä
Well we had a good neighbourhood, everything was okay.
nu yahši ğonšuluh varıdi yahšiidi äp
We were planting potatoes and living there.
